# 🧱 TRANSITIONS CONTRACT (IMPORTANT)

This becomes official progression routing.

Recommended structure:

```json id="v5w6ca"
"transitions": [
  {
    "id": "transition_001",

    "targetNodeId": "node_002",

    "kind": "default",

    "requirements": {
      "items": [],
      "flags": []
    },

    "effects": [],

    "priority": 0,

    "metadata": {}
  }
]
```

---

# 🧠 WHY THIS IS HUGE

Transitions become first-class systems.

That enables:

* hidden routes
* map travel
* portal animations
* branching
* lock/key systems
* timed escape routes
* multiplayer synchronization

without redesign later.

